02:38.933 --> 02:40.867
is an enchanted wonderland,

02:40.900 --> 02:44.067
an international crossroads,
a stewpot of neighborhoods

02:44.100 --> 02:46.200
filled with the languages,
cultures,

02:46.233 --> 02:48.867
traditions, and flavors
of many lands.

02:48.900 --> 02:50.233
Hey, how you doing?
Morning.

02:50.267 --> 02:52.367
My morning ritual
goes something like this:

02:52.400 --> 02:54.300
