when I'm out in Haifa ♪

07:37.267 --> 07:39.533
♪ Kick it with Muhammed
when I'm out in Jaffa ♪

07:39.567 --> 07:43.500
♪ Oh, no, we're in trouble ♪

07:43.533 --> 07:47.400
♪ TSA always wanna
burst my bubble ♪

07:47.433 --> 07:51.700
♪ Always get a random check
